    "Html": "<p>I&nbsp;have a user control with a datagrid and navigation (first/prev/next/last page)&nbsp;buttons at the bottom. The datagrid is public so that other windows can change columns, subscribe to events on the grid etc. When the item source is changed on the&nbsp;grid I need to recalculate the pagesizes&nbsp;etc. However, I can't workout when the items source is changed on the grid. I've worked around it by adding an items source property on the user control. But it won't work if the item source is set directly on the data grid.</p>\r\n<p>How can I know in my user control when the items source has been changed on&nbsp;the data grid?</p>",
